      <p>The <a href="ch73s03.html#MonstersAnimals9">badger</a> is a furry animal with a squat, powerful body. Its strong forelimbs are armed with long claws for digging. An adult <a href="ch73s03.html#MonstersAnimals9">badger</a> is 2 to 3 feet long and weighs 25 to 35 pounds.</p>
